{"tid":1407220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日起建立一個民族感","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T04:37:38.000Z","uid":54517,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3d6bebdebd17b6d7ef4001617a8bf851a73a5b","tid":1407220,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:59:50.000Z","msg":"希望大家今日起可以建立一個民族感,我有少少想法,日本,泡菜都比人有感覺就係佢民族好強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,所以外人好難埋堆,所以我覺得可以見以家呢場抗爭做多一步.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由大家都係香港人開始<br />\n<br />\n其實要做好簡單,平時多D幫手,開門又好,幫人攞野又好,咩都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,總知人地一講唔該,就即回一句&quot;大家香港人,唔使客氣&quot;慢慢建立一個民族初型,等下次如果再有抗爭嘅時候,大家都會有一種自己地方,唔可以比人攪嘅思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n<br />\n其實我都知自己打到1999,不過睇下呢個方向又行唔行到,你有想法,除時講底,得閒就覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2dc9b9ac8b844a0a4fc5d76fe5d60bd5e41896e","tid":1407220,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"民族自強！"},{"pid":"f4aef4960f370adb06371f32a6571f1240687f8d","tid":1407220,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2dc9b9ac8b844a0a4fc5d76fe5d60bd5e41896e","tid":1407220,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"民族自強！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f7af13bdc7765e130be4b285435f91d9e0ddea","tid":1407220,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"先自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2c6bd24a75e7e93a0f14e49daeec3b0832d6a5","tid":1407220,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T1